SlowQueryWithInputDatastoreParameters
public class SlowQueryDatastoreParameters<T>
extends DatastoreParameters
The input parameters required to report a slow datastore query on the TracedMethod. Do not use this class directly. Instead use DatastoreParameters.
Since:
3.36.0
